metadata.name: Five Deadly Rebels - Edition #1
metadata.description: The Five Deadly Rebels NFT gives holders exclusive access to unlock the complete digital ebook 'Five Deadly Rebels', a kung fu sci-fi novel featuring Rebels by Night Labs and Psychedelics Anonymous characters that holders own, as well as exclusive access to unlock the comic book adaptation in Summer 2023, and the audio book version in Fall 2023. More info on MysteryNovelNFT.com.
